race.comment: FONDLED (4) resumes having gone close in a couple of runs last time in. The two runner up finishes were on synthetic track but there's ability there and she should take catching in what looks a winnable affair. VEGA BLUES (3) resumes having been thereabouts in two harder runs last time in. He maps for a good run and should take holding out. ON MY OWN (1) has been solid in two runs back, finishing fourth in both. He was beaten under two lengths at Pakenham last time and should be ready to peak now. ROCK GLORY (5) put in a better effort last time at Great Western. She maps for every hope to measure up here.
